The '''Tsinimals''' were a race of [[Alien/Legends|alien]] species. In [[129 BBY]], they conquered the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Langhesa]] and enslaved the native [[Langhesi]] because they saw their biotechnology as an abomination to their gods. This led to a mass migration of Langhesi to other parts of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. However, [[Pirate/Legends|piracy]] and war weren't opposed by their gods. The Tsinimals were described as "graceful and intolerant."

